--------------
Privacy Policy
--------------
WhatAnime don't collect personal information such as your name or email. 
This app can store some preference setting to the app usage.
This settings don't be transferred outside of your device.

WhatAnime use the following permission:
   - WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE and READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE to read and select an image from your gallery.
   - INTERNET to use whatanime.ga API and other logs with Crashlytics(Fabric).
   - WAKE_LOCK to keep the screen on while searching operation is working.
